accessibility.text: Yuri's Night was created in 2000 by Loretta Hidalgo (later to be Whitesides), George Whitesides and Trish Garner.
The goal according to Loretta Hidalgo-Whitesides, "We’re trying to make space cool and appeal to younger generations and non-scientists."
